== Data Architecture

This section defines the physical data models, event schemas, and API request/response formats.

=== Domain Event Schemas (CloudEvents 1.0)

All domain events follow the https://cloudevents.io/[CloudEvents 1.0] specification for consistency and interoperability.

==== Event: SupportCaseCreated

Published when EngagementService successfully creates a Case in Salesforce.

[source,json]
----
{
  "specversion": "1.0",
  "type": "com.otr.engagement.support-case-created",
  "source": "urn:otr:engagement-service",
  "id": "a5f8c2e1-3d4b-4e9f-8c7a-1b2c3d4e5f6a",
  "time": "2026-01-07T14:30:00Z",
  "datacontenttype": "application/json",
  "data": {
    "caseNumber": "00123456",
    "contactId": "0034X00000ABCDEFG",
    "category": "App",
    "storeName": "OTR Adelaide",
    "timeOfVisit": "2026-01-07T12:00:00Z",
    "message": "App crashed when submitting feedback"
  }
}
----

==== Event: SupportCaseResolved

[source,json]
----
{
  "specversion": "1.0",
  "type": "com.otr.engagement.support-case-resolved",
  "source": "urn:salesforce:service-cloud",
  "id": "c7h0e4g3-5f6d-6g1h-0e9c-3d4e5f6g7h8c",
  "time": "2026-01-08T10:15:00Z",
  "datacontenttype": "application/json",
  "data": {
    "caseNumber": "00123456",
    "contactId": "0034X00000ABCDEFG",
    "status": "Closed",
    "resolution": "App crash fixed in version 2.5.1"
  }
}
----

