*Request*:
[source,json]
----
{
  "contactId": "0034X00000ABCDEFG",
  "category": "App",
  "storeName": "OTR Adelaide",
  "timeOfVisit": "2026-01-07T12:00:00Z",
  "contactPhoneNumber": "+61412345678",
